All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
App
This is the main class that starts the Tic-Tac-Toe game.
Board
The Board class represents the Tic-Tac-Toe board.
GameState
The GameState class stores information about the current state of the Tic-Tac-Toe game.
Player
This class represents a Player in a Tic-Tac-Toe game.
StateManager
The StateManager class is responsible for saving and loading the game state to and from a file.
Symbol
The Symbol enum represents the symbols used in Tic Tac Toe game.
